<div class="contentItem">
  <h1>Managing Users</h1>
  <h2></h2>

  <div class="contentItemBody">
    <p>
      As a blog admin user, you can manage user information stored in the security realm. This includes the ability
      to create new users, modify their user details (name, e-mail address, website and roles), remove users and reset passwords.
      To access these features, click the <a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/viewUsers.secureaction">Users</a> link.
    </p>

    <h3>Default password</h3>
    <p>
      The default password, for new users and password resets, is <code>password</code>.
    </p>

  </div>
</div>